    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small ornament of shiny metal or plastic in any shape, but usually round, and having a hole in the middle for use in fastening to clothing to create decorative effects. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
